OL,3,CFour-year-old boy among two killed in
OL,4,Cfour-car crash
OL,6,FA four-year-old boy and a 79-year-old
OL,7,Fwoman have died after a multi-vehicle
OL,8,Fcrash in Lincolnshire.
OL,10,FThe youngster, from Birmingham, was in
OL,11,Fa black Volvo XC60 which was involved
OL,12,Fin a collision with a grey MG 1300 on
OL,13,Fthe A157 close to Grimblethorpe,
OL,14,FLouth, on Sunday 15 March.
OL,16,FThe elderly woman, from Mablethorpe,
OL,17,Fwho was driving the MG, died a day
OL,18,Flater.
OL,20,FLincolnshire Police has now confirmed
OL,21,Fthe boy died on Monday 23 March.
